Assistant Manager Sales--Flooring‎
Morgan Chemicals
-
Karachi
We provide flooring solutions to Food, Pharma, Health and Hospital sectors for their Polyurethane and Epoxy Floors. Apart from core product selling of flooring, the required candidate will also be responsible for specialized products selling.
We are looking for Assistant Sales Manager for Karachi.
Candidate should have sales experience preferably in construction industry and should be technically qualified with excellent sales flair and knack of meeting.
Candidate should have strong communication skill (written / verbal).
Must have own conveyance.
